@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/raw-materials

### List all raw materials
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get raw material by ID (replace with actual UUID from create response)
GET {{baseUrl}}/REPLACE_WITH_RAW_MATERIAL_ID

### Create raw material
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Material X",
  "stockQuantity": 100
}

### Update raw material (replace with actual UUID)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/16C04BE6-4E23-4E0E-9854-E3BB025F6CF1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Material X Updated",
  "stockQuantity": 150
}

### Delete raw material (replace with actual UUID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/M001
